SOUTH CAROLINA
Pickens County

*Galax aphylla* L.

Botanical survey on west side of Eastatoe Creek
above High Bridge. Rich bluffs with a pH of 6.5 and
large mafic rocks along the creek. From Table Rock
go west about 8.0 miles, then right on S-143.
Follow road going north to powerline and park.
Walk powerline to creek and follow foot trail south
along Eastatoe Creek. 34.9658N & 82.8539W.

Ann Darr 2061
AB Pittman 06250302
Ron Ahle and Linda Lee                      25 June 2003
